Description: The GoogleArtProject is a place to explore museums from around the world- seeing and learning about the artwork they contain. It is a cool service- offering very high res images of the paintings- but not providing a machine-friendly access to the data shown. This server provides a wrapper around the HTML page for paintings and museums. It exposes part of the information using FOAF and Dublin Core ontologies and links the resource to DBpedia
